page.section:
Once you’ve found your timezone string, edit the timezone field in anchor/config/app.php (which should follow the format below, replacing Europe/London with your timezone string).
return array( ... 'timezone' => 'Europe/London',
Language Anchor supports multiple lannguages. To swithc between languages, edit the language variable in anchor/config/app.php'.
return array( ... 'language' => 'en_GB',
